---
// Footer.astro - Footer Component
---

<footer class="bg-slate-900 text-slate-400 border-t border-slate-800">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12">
      <div class="md:col-span-2">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-3 mb-6">
          <img src="/anwymed logo.png" alt="AnwyMed Logo" class="w-9 h-9">
          <span class="text-lg font-bold tracking-tight text-white">Anwy<span class="text-blue-400">Med</span></span>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-sm text-slate-400">
          Complete Clinic Management Software tailored perfectly for modern healthcare institutions. Engineered to unify diagnostics, patient records, inventory workflows, and billing operations under one secure ecosystem.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white tracking-wider text-sm uppercase mb-4">Product</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/#features" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Core Features</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#solutions" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Specialty Solutions</a></li>
          <li><a href="/#pricing" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Subscription Tiers</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white tracking-wider text-sm uppercase mb-4">Support & Trust</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-3 text-sm">
          <li><a href="/book-demo" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Connect Support</a></li>
          <li><a href="/cloud-security" class="hover:text-blue-400 transition-colors">Data Security Shield</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs">
      <div class="text-slate-500">
        <p>© 2026 AnwyMed. All rights reserved.</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Designed and developed by <a href="#" class="text-blue-400 hover:text-blue-300 transition-colors">Red Media Solutions</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex space-x-6">
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-slate-300">Privacy Protocols</a>
        <a href="#" class="hover:text-slate-300">Terms of Service</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
